## 3. 최적화 방안 (Before/After 코드)

### 최적화 1: N+1 쿼리 제거 - QueryDSL Fetch Join + Projection

```kotlin
// AFTER: 단일 쿼리로 해결
// CallMatchingQueryRepository.kt

@Repository
class CallMatchingQueryRepository(
    private val queryFactory: JPAQueryFactory
) {
    fun findMatchCandidatesWithProfile(
        excludeUserId: String,
        myGender: String,
        myAge: Int
    ): List<MatchCandidateDto> {
        return queryFactory
            .select(
                QMatchCandidateDto(
                    callWaiting.userId,
                    callWaiting.waitingSince,
                    userProfile.gender,
                    userProfile.age,
                    callPreference.ageMin,
                    callPreference.ageMax
                )
            )
            .from(callWaiting)
            .join(userProfile).on(userProfile.userId.eq(callWaiting.userId))
            .join(callPreference).on(callPreference.userId.eq(callWaiting.userId))
            .where(
                callWaiting.status.eq(WaitingStatus.WAITING),
                callWaiting.userId.ne(excludeUserId),
                userProfile.gender.ne(myGender),
                callPreference.ageMin.loe(myAge),
                callPreference.ageMax.goe(myAge)
            )
            .orderBy(callWaiting.waitingSince.asc()) // 오래 기다린 사람 우선
            .limit(20) // 후보군 제한
            .fetch()
    }
}
```

예상 효과: 201개 쿼리 -> 1개 쿼리. 응답 시간 500ms -> 30ms (94% 개선).

